data.description: Welcome to 217 Hansell Rd., a beautiful 3 bedrooms; 1 bathroom home in Lansdowne Borough! The main level features a gorgeous living room, dining room and kitchen all flooded with natural light and brand-new Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring. The custom kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and new white custom cabinetry. Upstairs you will find three large bedrooms and one full bathroom all with ample storage space. Come see this gorgeous home today!!!
